      "title": "SLC selects squad for SLvsAUS test series",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The\u00a0Sri Lanka Cricket Selection Committee has selected an 18-member squad to play in the 02 Match Test Series vs Australia.",
        "The test series, which is played under the ICC World Test Championship will commence on the 29th of June 2022, at the Galle International Cricket Stadium.",
        "Fuel protests continue today; Hatton residents allege no kerosene since 9th",
        "Prof. Rangita De Silva De Alwis elected as SL representative for CEDAW"
